<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fritz_Busch" title="Fritz Busch">Fritz Busch</a> (1945–1949)</li>
<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fritz_Reiner" title="Fritz Reiner">Fritz Reiner</a> (1949–1953)</li>
